m\": 2087, \"to\": 2099}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sekgodiso certainly did enough at her first Olympics to confirm she belongs at this level and there is much to be excited about this 22-year-old as she builds towards the 2028 Los Angeles Games.\", \"from\": 2102, \"to\": 2296, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Sekgodiso\", \"from\": 2102, \"to\": 2111}, {\"ngram\": \"her first Olympics\", \"from\": 2136, \"to\": 2154}, {\"ngram\": \"this level\", \"from\": 2181, \"to\": 2191}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2028 Los Angeles Games\", \"from\": 2269, \"to\": 2295}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She was forced a bit wide early on as the runners jostled for position and she sat alongside Ethiopia's Tsige Duguma in fourth spot, while Hodgkinson led Kenyan Mary Moraa through the bell in 58.4 seconds.\", \"from\": 2298, \"to\": 2503, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2391, \"end\": 2399, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethiopia\", \"score\": 0.9999997182340337, \"rank\": 1.893507078065537e-07, \"text\": \"Ethiopia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethiopia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethiopia\"}, {\"begin\": 2437, \"end\": 2447, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkinson_Minerals_Area\", \"score\": 0.9999964545312747, \"rank\": 3.545481068502687e-06, \"text\": \"Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkinson_Minerals_Area\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkinson_Minerals_Area\"}, {\"begin\": 2459, \"end\": 2463, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mary_II_of_England\", \"score\": 0.7000714927556055, \"rank\": 0.19378148933393155, \"text\": \"Mary\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mary_II_of_England\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mary_II_of_England\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the runners\", \"from\": 2336, \"to\": 2347}, {\"ngram\": \"position\", \"from\": 2360, \"to\": 2368}, {\"ngram\": \"fourth spot\", \"from\": 2418, \"to\": 2429}, {\"ngram\": \"the bell\", \"from\": 2478, \"to\": 2486}, {\"ngram\": \"58.4 seconds\", \"from\": 2490, \"to\": 2502}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The speed was injected down the back straight and Sekgodiso went with the leaders.\", \"from\": 2505, \"to\": 2587, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The speed\", \"from\": 2505, \"to\": 2514}, {\"ngram\": \"the back straight\", \"from\": 2533, \"to\": 2550}, {\"ngram\": \"Sekgodiso\", \"from\": 2555, \"to\": 2564}, {\"ngram\": \"the leaders\", \"from\": 2575, \"to\": 2586}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, she was kept wide around the far turn, although still had a puncher's chance entering the final straight.\", \"from\": 2589, \"to\": 2703, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the far turn\", \"from\": 2623, \"to\": 2635}, {\"ngram\": \"a puncher's chance\", \"from\": 2656, \"to\": 2674}, {\"ngram\": \"the final straight\", \"from\": 2684, \"to\": 2702}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's when the race started to tell and she slipped back through the field, knowing her chances had evaporated.\", \"from\": 2704, \"to\": 2816, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 2716, \"to\": 2724}, {\"ngram\": \"the field\", \"from\": 2770, \"to\": 2779}, {\"ngram\": \"her chances\", \"from\": 2789, \"to\": 2800}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The plan was to stick with the girls for as long as I could.\", \"from\": 2818, \"to\": 2879, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The plan\", \"from\": 2819, \"to\": 2827}, {\"ngram\": \"the girls\", \"from\": 2846, \"to\": 2855}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I know I am not good in the final 100m and when I saw the girls coming past me, I thought I must just keep my head up and keep going.\", \"from\": 2880, \"to\": 3013, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the final 100m\", \"from\": 2904, \"to\": 2918}, {\"ngram\": \"the girls\", \"from\": 2934, \"to\": 2943}, {\"ngram\": \"my head\